item.title: My First post- Winter is coming!
item.description: As of today it’s the 23rd of November. This means that Winter is coming… It’s soon to be December, and of course this means we are ending 2015 and coming into a new year in January. This time of the year always reminds me of 3 things: Cold dark mornings...
